text: ( Source : NHL - National Hockey League ) SAGINAW, Mich. - Travis Barron scored three times and Travis Konecny had four assists as the Ottawa 67's came from behind to defeat the host Saginaw Spirit 6-4 on Sunday in Ontario Hockey League
